Davenport.E. P. Adler House: The E.P. Adler House, is a c. 1910 historic house located in the central part of Davenport, Iowa, United States. It has been individually listed on the National Register of Historic Places since 1983 and as a contributing property in the Vander Veer Park Historic District since 1984. It has been on the Davenport Register of Historic Properties since 2008.
